    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行管委纳格尔对模糊的“中性”利率目标和美国关税损害表示担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/ecb-should-cut-rates-gradually-not-target-neutral-nagel-argues-2025-02-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国央行行长纳格尔周三表示，欧洲央行应逐步放松政策，而不是以难以定义的“中性”利率为目标，但如果全球贸易战爆发，欧洲央行需要做好为欧洲而战的准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/ecb-should-cut-rates-gradually-not-target-neutral-nagel-argues-2025-02-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 17:33:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
