      <title>瑞信破产后，美国银行瑞士团队规模扩大一倍</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bofa-doubles-banking-team-switzerland-amid-shifting-regulatory-landscape-2025-02-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行首席执行官表示，该银行已将其瑞士银行团队的规模扩大了一倍，抓住瑞信破产后瑞士银行业市场动荡带来的潜在机会，抢占市场份额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bofa-doubles-banking-team-switzerland-amid-shifting-regulatory-landscape-2025-02-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 15:45:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度储备银行解除对 Kotak 发行信用卡和以数字方式登记客户的禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/indias-central-bank-removes-restrictions-kotak-mahindra-bank-onboarding-2025-02-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度储备银行周三表示，已解除了对科塔克马辛德拉银行实施的十个月禁令，禁止该银行以数字方式接纳新客户和发行新信用卡，原因是该银行的 IT 基础设施存在缺陷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/indias-central-bank-removes-restrictions-kotak-mahindra-bank-onboarding-2025-02-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 11:53:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
